= Coding style =

* Restrict the line length to at most 80 characters.

* Indentation should consist of 4 spaces (2 spaces are also accepted).

* Don't use tab characters.

* Use UTF-8 characters, no other encodings.

* Don't add whitespace at line endings.

* Terminate lines with linefeed (LF). Don't use Windows line terminators.

* Terminate a file with exactly one linefeed.
